window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Five rules. Five ways to die. And one cockroach that just won't quit.</b></p> <p>Nathaniel finally gets himself a master, and a certain lynthari to suffer through it all with him.</p> <p>The 5th floor starts all over, but this time with a cheat code in the form of a living nuclear bomb breathing down Nathaniel’s neck and training him so that he might one day be comparable to the pets the noble ladies used to have.</p> <p>This time, all roads lead to the pyramid, an ancient Champion’s creation built to turn the heat of a volcano into mana. The short discipleship concludes deep below, inside the chamber full of molten metal.</p> <p>But even after that, things don’t slow down. Nathaniel finally enters Beyond, meets his Handler, and learns more about this place that is more mysterious than it initially seems.</p> <p>There are messed-up Challenges to be declared, intruders into mind space, the 6th floor of the tutorial, the Mana Desert full of deadly white sand, a cute golden retriever, and more.</p> <p><b>The adventure continues in Book 5 of </b><b><i>HELL DIFFICULTY TUTORIAL</i></b><b>, faster, messier, and far from done. There is still too much left unanswered. Nathaniel must outsmart the odds, survive, and emerge stronger than anyone else!</b></p> <p><b>With more than 10 million views as a web serial, this definitive version is perfect for fans of </b><b><i>The Primal Hunter</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>Defiance of the Fall</i></b><b>, and</b><b><i> Apocalypse: Generic System</i></b><b>. Grab your copy today!</b></p>"; 
